@wp.kernel
def expr_dbnral(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.77)) / v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.15 - v1 + 0.33) / (v1 + 0.41 / v1 + 0.3)))
    data[tid] = v0
